'''Switzerland''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 2000''' in [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]]. [[Jane Bogaert]] represented Switzerland with the song "[[La vita cos'e|La vita cos'è]]". They scored 14 points (the highest being 6 from Netherlands) finishing 20th.

